Package: miaoseq
Title: MiaoSeq - A comprehensive pipeline for sequencing data analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tomoyuki", "Furuta", , "f.tomoyuki@okayama-u.ac.jp", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Tomoyuki Furuta <f.tomoyuki@okayama-u.ac.jp>
Maintainer: Tomoyuki Furuta <f.tomoyuki@okayama-u.ac.jp>
Description: MiaoSeq provides a comprehensive pipeline for sequencing data analysis including basecalling, demultiplexing, alignment, and edit calling. The package integrates multiple bioinformatics tools and provides streamlined workflows for processing sequencing data. Optimized with Rcpp for improved performance.
